def: One of the tribe of Judah; a member of the kingdom of Judah; aJew. Kitto.
A plant which keeps its leaves green through the winter.
Pertaining to, or resembling, the pedipalps.
A kind of pump for exhausting air from a vessel or closedspace; also, a pump to condense air of force in into a closed space.
Pertaining to, or containing, columbium or niobium; niobic.Columbic acid (Chem.), a weak acid derived from columbic or niobicoxide, Nb2O5; -- called also niobic acid.
A place for exit; an outlet; hence, a market for goods.The débouchés were ordered widened to afford easy egress. TheCentury.
One who, or that which, whirls.
A thick plain silk, generally black, and used for clerical.Simmonds.
